item.description:
There were days that i did not like XSL because it seemed to be impossible to insert a value inside an attribute. For example:
&lt;form action=&#34;&lt;xsl:value-of select=&#34;/page/action&#34;/&gt;&#34; method=&#34;post&#34;&gt; Today i&rsquo;ve seen that other people also struggle with this issue. So here is the solution:
&lt;form action=&#34;{/page/action}&#34; method=&#34;post&#34;&gt;
